This folder contains the Nova agent tools for Windows system.

IPchanger:
This tool is in charge of configuring a new VM, including IP address & software installation.
It is written by Huang Gang (herokuankuan@gmail.com)

ConfigFTP:
ConfigFTP  is used to simplify configuration process of FtpDrive, which is used to mount FTP
as a Windows network Driver. The FtpDrive software is included in the ConfigFTP source dir.
It is written by Gao Tao (gaotao1987@gmail.com)
